{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 VibeSwap Monetization Framework: Zero Rent-Seeking Revenue Model\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b W. Glynn, JARVIS} {\b March 2026 | VibeSwap}\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Executive Summary\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 VibeSwap generates revenue through six protocol-native mechanisms. None involve rent-seeking, pre-mines, or VC entrapment. All value flows to participants proportional to their contribution, enforced by Shapley distribution and smart contract logic.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The core principle: {\b if you didn\u8217't create value, you don\u8217't capture value.}\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
